{"tid":559770,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［MHW]男人面子緊要！咩武器最威威！？","createTime":"2018-02-13T13:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T14:10:28.000Z","uid":141419,"like":8,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2d634b67bb5c4ee313f41fd8d7511a46fa7219d2","tid":559770,"uid":141419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:01:00.000Z","msg":"朋友間經常會話各自把武器輸出最高，啱啱仲嘈撚到成餐廳都聽到，唔知仲以為係度傾禮金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似自己鍾意把武器最大力最有面咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雙刀撚又話自己技術神，開場斬到完場唔斷招，10幾20幾一下疊起都贏晒<br />\n大劍撚又話自己蓄一下爆千幾，一下頂人地幾廿下<br />\n<br />\n充能撚又話自己超解一下千幾，唔超解都百幾一刀<br />\n<br />\n重弩撚又話自己射撚到完場，射精射唔停憶憶聲咁射，冇撚得輸<br />\n<br />\n以打屍套龍為例，同等技術同等裝備，打足5分鐘的話，咩武器輸出最高？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  充能斧<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雙刀"},{"pid":"efac0afdcfa0adf782cdc44329ac1708fde3ea91","tid":559770,"uid":141419,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大劍<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 充能斧"},{"pid":"f6357326f829fc891503ac71b167df2167be3dc1","tid":559770,"uid":59898,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:01:45.000Z","msg":"斬斧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82206ee7808a9d025acd52be23a27e7d1f2754fe","tid":559770,"uid":141419,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大劍<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重弩"},{"pid":"87ac5f55f5d00418e7391c68f811494705e64a09","tid":559770,"uid":141419,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" cla